name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Copy or migrate to Wix Editor

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Copy or migrate existing site design and text to Wix Editor

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Copy or migrate to Wix Editor extension allows you to copy (or migrate) any formatting from any website into Wix Editor (Classic or Studio). While it is typically preferable to create your own design, in certain cases, you may want to copy an existing design. This extension lets you reuse existing designs in Wix Editor.
